{
  "chapter": 197,
  "chapter_summary": "第一百九十七章《诡幻多变》。寇仲思虑洛阳局势，认为王世充难成大器，李密因李世民威胁不肯轻易犯险。他灵光一闪，悟出沈落雁杀独孤霸是为了破坏独孤阀与铁勒人的关系，但独孤阀不会信他。寇仲心萌退意，决定先找虚行之。徐子陵与沈落雁在天津桥附近会面，沈落雁透露独孤霸尸身已被发现，嫁祸于徐子陵和跋锋寒，并劝他尽快离开洛阳。徐子陵深感不安。寇仲被宋蒙秋拉去参加王世充为尚秀芳设的午宴，席间欧阳希夷特意让座给寇仲。彤彤找到徐子陵，告知独孤霸尸身被吊在天津桥，独孤峰反应异常平静更令人担忧，又透露王世充阵营中有内奸与独孤峰暗中勾结。徐子陵惊觉事态严重，决定立即寻找寇仲商议对策。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今趟又要怎样害我们呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "苍天为何如此作弄人，将你和我安排在敌对的立场上？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "走吧！王世充气数已尽，迟点你们连走都走不了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "告诉我，我怎样才可分辨你的提议是恶意还是善意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "让我告诉你一件事，独孤霸的尸身已被发现，从他身上的伤痕，几可肯定是你和跋锋寒下手的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "text": "好一条嫁祸的妙计！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "每趟要害你时，我心中的痛苦实不足为外人道，你明白吗？你还是走吧！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_luo_yan",
      "speaker_name": "沈落雁",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "要说的话已说了！连不该说的都说出来，大丈夫能屈能伸。子陵保重！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄弟，尚书大人正要找你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "text": "宋将军这两天定是很忙，否则我怎会有像很久没见过宋将军的感觉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这些日子我们连睡觉的时间都没有，所以连尚书大人都要找些东西来松弛一下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "text": "我真想不到有甚么事情可令我们这些没一觉好睡的人能忘忧无虑。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然是女人，还得是最标致的美人儿，声色艺俱全，美得能令人连老爹姓甚么都忘掉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "text": "谁家美人儿有这种魅力和威力。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然是有天下第一名妓之称的尚秀芳，除了她谁还配称声、色、艺俱全呢？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "王大人知她明晚唱完荣凤祥那台戏后便要入关中，所以千方百计把她请来，还摆了两桌酒席，所以嘱我们找你去趁热闹。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "text": "现在是甚么时候，我刚刚饮饱食醉，想塞多半个包子都无能为力。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄弟是否在说笑，醉翁之意，岂在酒菜？尚美人出名爱睡午觉，所以若要约她，只能在未时之后，来吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "text": "我要先去方便一下。免得入席后看得精采之时却欲离难离就不妙之极了。哈！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_meng_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "宋蒙秋",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那待会见吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐爷不认得彤彤了吗？那天徐爷和刘帅见面时，人家还给你斟茶哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "你的装扮术是否诸葛德威兄亲传？一点没有女扮男装的破绽。我还记得刘大哥赞你的飞刀了得呢。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "想不到徐爷这么没有架子，初见你时，人家还有点怕你哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "我有甚么可怕的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不是真的怕，只是觉得徐爷是那种不爱说话，永远都要和别人保持一段距离那副样子的人。你知啦！徐爷的名气又那么大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "那只是我装出来唬小女孩的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "你没有随刘大哥北返吗？这样留你下来太危险了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此处太露形迹，徐爷可否随彤彤到别处说话？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "没有问题，不过我有要事须处理，所以不能花太多时间。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只一会使成。马儿可留在这里，我们自有人为你看管。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇先生请到这里来！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "还以为你会错过这个盛会，见你这么有缘，就赐你坐这凤座旁的龙位，近水楼台，打后就要看你的造化！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "看来王公仍非那么够朋友，若王公肯在今早告诉我约得尚小姐，那即使独孤峰合家老少拦在皇城入口，我也要打进来哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲你有所不知了，秀芳姑娘是直至个许时辰前才通知我肯来赴宴，你说我今早能通知你甚么呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_xuan_ying",
      "speaker_name": "王玄应",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "爹现在的面子比天还大，本来秀芳小姐今趟到东都来是只肯唱两台的，其他一概拒绝。今次破例，肯定会招来很多人的羡慕哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "顾着说话，差点忘了给寇先生引见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳希夷",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "仲小兄该怎样谢我？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_xi_yi",
      "text": "前辈为小子做了甚么好事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_xi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳希夷",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你的座位是老夫特别让出来给你的，你说该否谢我？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "独孤霸是否徐爷下手的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "我本想般他，但下手的却是另有其人，但现在怎都脱不了关系。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "独孤霸臭名远播，他的死讯只会大快人心。但此事最奇怪处，就是不觉独孤峰似有甚么显着行动，令我反更为徐爷担心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "他们是甚么时候发现独孤霸尸身的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "该是昨天三更时份，他的尸体被巡更的人发现，吊在天津桥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "有谓不是你死，就是我亡。徐爷和寇爷最好先发制人，否则必会吃亏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "我正要找寇仲商量此事，你知否宋金刚落脚的地点？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "你的消息倒灵通。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这正是我们留在此处的任务。还有一个非常重要的消息须知会徐爷，照我们猜测，王世充的阵营中该有一个与独孤峰暗中勾结的内奸。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tong_tong",
      "text": "何有此言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这是从一些蛛丝马迹推测出来的。坦白说，宫城内也有我们的眼线，例如杨侗的大臣元文都一向贪生怕死，可是即管王世充枕重兵于皇城，他仍是照样风花雪月，谈话间不但显得毫无忌惮，还曾说过晓得王世充的整盘计划。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_tong",
      "speaker_name": "彤彤",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只看独孤阀要不择手段地对付寇爷，便知独孤峰清楚是寇爷为王世充运筹帷幄了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要立即去找寇仲。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    }
  ],
